speaker: Cesar De la Torre Llorente
title: Build Recap | What’s new in Azure Machine Learning Automated ML
description:
Cesar De la Torre Llorente is here to highlight what's new in Azure Machine Learning Automated ML. He'll cover AutoML “white box” in action: Leverage Automated ML model's training code generation in Azure Machine Learning and Automated ML as part of Azure Machine Learning Python SDK v2 and CLI v2.
